私は終わるまで 染まっていくんでしょう
I will probably keep being dyed until it's over.

6
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:21,000
私は怖がりで 知らないことには 手を付けず
I'm a coward; I won't touch things I don't know.

7
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:25,200
誰かがやって来て 毒見をするまで 待っていた
I waited for someone to come and taste the poison first.

8
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:29,400
知ることは単純で マニュアル通りの 生活を
Learning is simple; leading a life according to the manual,

9
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:34,000
来る日も淡々と 過ごしていた
I've been spending my days indifferently.

10
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:38,200
そうや さあ さあ 昨日も私もこうだった
That's right, come on, come on, yesterday I was like this too.

11
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:42,500
そうや さあ さあ
That's right, come on, come on.

12
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:47,300
弱い音を吐いてる 薄っぺらい人間です
I'm a shallow human who utters weak sounds.

13
00:02:47,300 --> 00:02:51,500
一歩前に出るのは やめときます 絡まれたくないからさ
I'll refrain from taking a step forward because I don't want to get involved.

14
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:55,700
描いた理想像に 現実味がないから
Because the ideal image I painted isn't realistic,

15
00:02:55,700 --> 00:03:00,000
近づけないよう 生きておきます 明日も同じを 過ごしておきます
I'll live so as not to get close to it, and spend tomorrow the same way.

16
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:13,800
路地裏の真ん中で いつもの夕日を 薄目で眺めて
In the middle of a back alley, gazing at the usual sunset with narrowed eyes,

17
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:18,100
胸の中で呟いた いつまで続くんだろう
I whispered in my heart, 'I wonder how long this will last.'

18
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:22,400
そうや さあ さあ 昨日も夕飯これだった
That's right, come on, come on, yesterday's dinner was this too.

19
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:26,500
そうや さあ さあ
That's right, come on, come on.

20
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:31,500
自虐で切りが悪い 惨めな人間です
I'm a miserable human, unending in my self-deprecation.

21
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:35,800
一歩後ろに下がって 逃げときます 目立ちたくなんかないからさ
I'll take a step back and run away, because I don't want to stand out at all.

22
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:40,000
描いた理想像に 現実味がないから
Because the ideal image I painted isn't realistic,

23
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:44,200
近づけないよう 生きておきます 明日も同じを 過ごしておきます
I'll live so as not to get close to it, and spend tomorrow the same way.

24
00:04:05,100 --> 00:04:09,300
弱い音を吐いてる 薄っぺらい人間です
I'm a shallow human who utters weak sounds.

25
00:04:09,300 --> 00:04:13,600
一歩前に出るのは やめときます 絡まれたくないからさ
I'll refrain from taking a step forward because I don't want to get involved.

26
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:17,800
溜息ばっかついて 突き足りないの
I do nothing but sigh, yet it's never enough.

27
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:22,000
きっとそう上手くは いかないけどさ 試しにちょっと 生きてみよう
It surely won't go that smoothly, but let's try living a little.

28
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:57,400
鉄の弾が 正義の証明 貫けば 英雄に近づいた
Iron bullets are proof of justice. If they pierce through, I've come closer to being a hero.

29
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:57,500
悪魔の子 作詞・作曲: ヒグチアイ
Akuma no Ko / Lyrics & Composition: Higuchi Ai

30
00:04:57,400 --> 00:05:00,000
その目を閉じて 触れてみれば
If I close my eyes and try to touch it...

31
00:05:00,008 --> 00:05:05,108
同じ形 同じ体温の悪魔
Devils of the same shape and the same body temperature.

32
00:05:05,408 --> 00:05:08,208
僕はダメで あいつはいいの？
Am I no good and they're okay?

33
00:05:08,508 --> 00:05:10,908
そこに壁があっただけなのに
When there was simply a wall there.

34
00:05:11,108 --> 00:05:13,408
生まれてしまった 運命嘆くな
Don't lament the fate of being born.

35
00:05:13,708 --> 00:05:14,908
僕らはみんな
Because we are all

36
00:05:15,108 --> 00:05:17,008
自由なんだから
Free.

37
00:05:17,308 --> 00:05:22,208
鳥のように 羽があれば
If I had wings like a bird,

38
00:05:22,508 --> 00:05:27,208
どこへだって 行けるけど
I could go anywhere.

39
00:05:27,508 --> 00:05:32,108
帰る場所が なければ
But if I have no place to return to,

40
00:05:32,408 --> 00:05:37,008
きっとどこへも行けない
I surely can't go anywhere.

41
00:05:37,408 --> 00:05:42,508
ただただ生きるのは嫌だ
I don't want to just exist.

42
00:05:43,008 --> 00:05:48,008
世界は残酷だ
The world is cruel.

43
00:05:48,308 --> 00:05:53,308
それでも君を愛すよ
Even so, I will love you.

44
00:05:53,608 --> 00:05:58,708
なにを犠牲にしても
No matter what I have to sacrifice.

45
00:05:59,008 --> 00:06:04,008
それでも君を守るよ
Even so, I will protect you.

46
00:06:04,308 --> 00:06:08,508
間違いだとしても 疑ったりしない
Even if it's a mistake, I won't doubt it.

47
00:06:08,808 --> 00:06:14,008
正しさとは自分のこと 強く信じることだ
Righteousness is to believe strongly in oneself.

48
00:06:24,008 --> 00:06:29,508
鉄の雨が降り頻る情景 テレビの中 映画に見えたんだ
The scene of iron rain falling incessantly; it looked like a movie on TV.

49
00:06:29,808 --> 00:06:34,608
戦争なんて愚かな凶暴 関係ない 知らない国の話
War is such foolish brutality; it's an irrelevant story of a country I don't know.

50
00:06:34,908 --> 00:06:40,108
それならなんで あいつ憎んで 黒い気持ち 隠しきれない理由
Then why do I hate them? The reason I can't hide these dark feelings.

51
00:06:40,408 --> 00:06:46,008
説明だってできやしないんだ 僕らはなんて矛盾ばっかなんだ
I can't even explain it; we are just full of contradictions.

52
00:07:07,408 --> 00:07:18,208
この言葉も訳されれば 本当の意味は伝わらない
Even if these words are translated, the true meaning won't be conveyed.

53
00:07:18,508 --> 00:07:27,508
信じるのはその目を開いて 触れた世界だけ
All I believe in is the world I saw and touched with my own eyes.

54
00:07:27,808 --> 00:07:33,008
ただただ生きるのは嫌だ
I don't want to just exist.

55
00:07:36,508 --> 00:07:41,508
世界は残酷だ
The world is cruel.

56
00:07:41,808 --> 00:07:47,008
それでも君を愛すよ
Even so, I will love you.

57
00:07:47,308 --> 00:07:52,208
なにを犠牲にしても
No matter what I have to sacrifice.

58
00:07:52,508 --> 00:07:57,508
それでも君を守るよ
Even so, I will protect you.

59
00:07:57,808 --> 00:08:02,508
選んだ人の影 捨てたものの屍
The shadows of those chosen, the corpses of those cast aside.

60
00:08:02,808 --> 00:08:08,008
気づいたんだ 自分の中 育つのは悪魔の子
I realized that what's growing inside of me is a child of evil.

61
00:08:08,308 --> 00:08:14,008
正義の裏 犠牲の中 心には悪魔の子
Behind justice, amidst sacrifice, there is a child of evil in my heart.

62
00:08:42,508 --> 00:08:47,508
そっと振り返って 奇跡どうしたって光って
Looking back softly, the miracle shines no matter what.

63
00:08:47,808 --> 00:08:52,508
ありふれて君が いつだってスーパーヒーロー
Though it's common, you are always a superhero.

64
00:09:00,508 --> 00:09:05,208
いつもポンコツだった私 止めなくて 未完成
I've always been a klutz, don't stop me, I'm incomplete.

65
00:09:05,508 --> 00:09:10,508
アヒルの子はアヒルのまま 飛べないなんてさ
Saying that an ugly duckling stays a duckling and can't fly.

66
00:09:11,008 --> 00:09:15,908
正しさなんて放っておいて 君となんかちょっと似ていて
Leaving righteousness aside, I'm somewhat similar to you.

67
00:09:16,208 --> 00:09:21,208
凸凹だからジャストに噛み合うパズルピース
Puzzle pieces that fit just right because they're uneven.

68
00:09:21,508 --> 00:09:26,508
繋げたい 繋げたい 届かない言葉も
I want to connect, I want to connect even the words that won't reach.

69
00:09:26,808 --> 00:09:31,208
いつかは誰かの何かに なりたいから
Because someday I want to become something to someone.

70
00:09:31,508 --> 00:09:36,208
Crazy, Noisy, 夢の中
Crazy, noisy, in a dream.

71
00:09:36,508 --> 00:09:40,508
夢を見せて
Show me a dream.

72
00:09:40,808 --> 00:09:42,008
Always going!

73
00:09:42,208 --> 00:09:47,208
何千回 何万回 膝をついても
No matter how many thousands or tens of thousands of times I fall on my knees.

74
00:09:47,508 --> 00:09:52,208
最大限 アイラブユーで立ち上がれるから
I can stand up with a maximum 'I love you'.

75
00:09:52,508 --> 00:09:58,008
とびきりのサンキュー 消えないハッピーも勇気も
An extraordinary 'thank you', for the happiness and courage that won't fade.

76
00:10:00,016 --> 00:10:01,401
...塗り潰しちゃって
...Paint over it all.

77
00:10:01,401 --> 00:10:06,016
大失敗も後悔さえ愛せるなら
If I can love even my greatest failures and regrets,

78
00:10:06,016 --> 00:10:10,016
背中には君という羽
I'll have wings known as "you" on my back.

79
00:10:20,957 --> 00:10:25,580
チックタック追い越して いつもどこか乾いた焦燥感
Overtaking the tick-tock, always feeling a parched sense of impatience.

80
00:10:25,580 --> 00:10:30,516
隣で走る君と 織りなすレゾナンスストーリー
A resonance story woven together with you running beside me.

81
00:10:41,630 --> 00:10:46,352
君の色が私を塗り替えて
Your colors repaint me,

82
00:10:46,352 --> 00:10:51,864
壊れかけの音で響くから
Because they resonate with a half-broken sound.

83
00:10:51,864 --> 00:10:57,076
お伽話の続きをまだ描きたいんだよ
I still want to draw the continuation of the fairy tale.

84
00:10:57,076 --> 00:11:02,529
連れて行くよ
I'll take you with me.

85
00:11:05,174 --> 00:11:12,766
(Vocalizing)

86
00:11:13,016 --> 00:11:14,516
Always going

87
00:11:14,516 --> 00:11:19,004
何全回何万回迷い込んでも
No matter how many thousands or tens of thousands of times I get lost,

88
00:11:19,004 --> 00:11:24,491
最大級 I love you な君がいるから
Because I have you, whom I love to the maximum degree.

89
00:11:24,491 --> 00:11:29,491
本日スペシャルな Thank you さぁ手を持って
A special "Thank you" for today, now take my hand.

90
00:11:29,491 --> 00:11:34,978
運命も手繰り寄せて
And pull even destiny towards us.

91
00:11:34,978 --> 00:11:40,466
もうバイバイも涙も忘れないよ
I won't forget the goodbyes or the tears anymore.

92
00:11:40,466 --> 00:11:45,953
止められなかった私のこの背中には
On this back of mine that couldn't be stopped,

93
00:11:45,953 --> 00:11:50,953
君という羽
Are wings known as "you."

94
00:12:19,513 --> 00:12:25,064
描いた未来の景色がここにある
The scenery of the future I drew is right here.

95
00:12:25,064 --> 00:12:30,423
弱さも抱きしめていくから
Because I'll keep embracing even my weaknesses.

96
00:12:30,423 --> 00:12:35,353
広げた翼が輝いていく
The wings I've spread are starting to shine.

97
00:12:35,353 --> 00:12:39,248
旅立て明日
Set out for tomorrow.

98
00:12:56,607 --> 00:13:00,688
等身大の私を映してたい ただ
I just want to reflect my true self.

99
00:13:00,688 --> 00:13:05,769
望む瞬間衝動になってんだ くだらないとさ
The moment I desire it, it becomes an impulse. They say it's trivial.

100
00:13:05,769 --> 00:13:10,534
曇りきっていく目をして
With eyes that are becoming completely clouded,

101
00:13:10,534 --> 00:13:15,839
可能性だって夢を見てみたいのに
I want to try and see the dream of possibilities.

102
00:13:15,839 --> 00:13:21,050
ずっとわかっていたんだけど 言葉は浮いてる対象に
I've known it all along, but words are just floating targets.

103
00:13:21,050 --> 00:13:26,131
大袈裟だって思ってるんでしょ
You think I'm exaggerating, don't you?

104
00:13:26,131 --> 00:13:31,300
ずっと黙っていたんだけど 心ってやっぱ正直だ
I've been keeping quiet, but the heart is honest after all.

105
00:13:31,300 --> 00:13:36,605
打ち明けたい訳、感じ気がしてる
I feel like I have a reason to confide.

106
00:13:37,016 --> 00:13:41,516
ここだよ響かせて
I'm right here, make it resonate.

107
00:13:41,516 --> 00:13:47,316
掲げた鼓動で 描くの... 終わらないでしょう
Drawing with the heartbeat I've held up... it won't end, right?

108
00:13:47,316 --> 00:13:52,016
灯になっていく
It's becoming a light.

109
00:13:52,016 --> 00:13:55,353
何度も奪われ繰り返し 意志の傷痕に
Repeatedly robbed, on the scars of my will,

110
00:13:55,353 --> 00:13:57,016
誓った
I made a vow.

111
00:14:06,347 --> 00:14:10,473
失敗後悔は泣いて溜息の音がしてる
Failures and regrets are crying, making the sound of a sigh.

112
00:14:10,473 --> 00:14:15,600
現状に不満はない 飲み込んだ気でいたんだ
I have no complaints with the status quo. I thought I'd swallowed it all.

113
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:20,317
泡、忘れないように
So as not to forget the fleeting bubbles,

114
00:14:20,317 --> 00:14:25,444
降臨祭 もう汚されないように
Advent festival, so that I won't be tainted anymore.

115
00:14:25,444 --> 00:14:30,328
もっと笑っていたいんだもん 大人になっていく代償に
Because I want to smile more, as a price for becoming an adult.

116
00:14:30,328 --> 00:14:35,454
あなただってきっと思ってるんでしょ
You're probably thinking the same thing, aren't you?

117
00:14:35,454 --> 00:14:40,454
ちゃんと分かっていたんだけど 心ってやっぱ正直だ
I understood it well, but the heart is honest after all.

118
00:14:40,454 --> 00:14:45,706
失せなくなった痛みを 感じ気がしてる
I feel the pain that won't go away.

119
00:14:46,016 --> 00:14:50,516
照らされたこの場所で
In this place that's lit up,

120
00:14:50,516 --> 00:14:56,516
咲かせた手ほら 描くの... 終わらないでしょう
Look at the hand I've made bloom, drawing... it won't end, right?

121
00:14:56,516 --> 00:14:59,016
我儘待っている
Selfishness is waiting.

122
00:15:00,024 --> 00:15:01,324
取り戻した
I regained it

123
00:15:01,324 --> 00:15:03,224
日々の傷跡に
in the scars of everyday life

124
00:15:03,224 --> 00:15:05,124
誓った
I swore

125
00:15:13,024 --> 00:15:19,424
心よ響かせて
Let my heart resonate

126
00:15:22,724 --> 00:15:29,324
心を響かせて
Let my heart resonate

127
00:15:30,424 --> 00:15:33,424
ずっと
forever

128
00:15:35,024 --> 00:15:37,324
心だよ響かせて
