129
00:15:37,324 --> 00:15:39,124
掲げたこの腕
This arm I raised

130
00:15:39,124 --> 00:15:41,324
Never mind でしょ？
Never mind, right?

131
00:15:41,324 --> 00:15:44,224
右に左に 繋がっていく
Connecting right and left

132
00:15:44,224 --> 00:15:47,324
何度も
Over and over again

133
00:15:47,324 --> 00:15:49,424
奪われたって 取り返した
Even if it's taken away, I'll take it back

134
00:15:49,424 --> 00:15:51,524
日々の傷跡に
in the scars of everyday life

135
00:15:51,524 --> 00:15:53,624
誓った
I swore

136
00:16:13,024 --> 00:16:15,524
あっ、はい！　はぁ……
Ah, yes! *sigh*...

137
00:16:15,524 --> 00:16:17,324
皆さん！
Everyone!

138
00:16:17,324 --> 00:16:21,024
というわけで、本日は……えー
And so, today...

139
